com.burstly.lib.ui
Interface IBurstlyAdListener

All Superinterfaces:
IBurstlyRichMedia
All Known Subinterfaces:
IInternalBurstlyAdListener
public interface IBurstlyAdListener
extends IBurstlyRichMedia

This interface is used to get ad receiving callbacks from BurstlyView. Keep in mind that all these callbacks are being called in UI thread. So do not make any kind of "heavy" operations inside.
